Here is a cheat sheet for some of the functions in the Adafruit Circuit Playground Library

Inputs

CircuitPlayground.lightSensor();
CircuitPlayground.mic.soundPressureLevel(10);
CircuitPlayground.temperature();
CircuitPlayground.temperatureF();

Outputs

Speaker
CircuitPlayground.playTone(500, 100);


Neopixels

Set Pixel Color for a specific pixel
CircuitPlayground.setPixelColor(0, 255,   0,   0);

Clear Pixels / Turn Them Off
CircuitPlayground.clearPixels();

Turn All the Pixels to a Color Using a For Loop
  for (int i = 0; i < 10; i++){CircuitPlayground.setPixelColor(i, 128,   0,   128)}
